snippet.title: Heretic Hunt Gameplay - CE3 2015
snippet.description:
Heretic Hunt is a short campaign mod that takes the player through a story line that takes placed during the events of the heretics in Halo 2's timeline. Discover a new gas mine, explore the moon Basis, and follow both the Heretics and Covenant. 

From: Spiral, and Heempy 

See more CE3 at http://haloce3.com/ce32015/
